This Doll Is Dangerous | Evil Little Things | Thriller Horror Movie

A leprechaun spawned from the depths of hell, a malicious doll born of your worst nightmares and an evil toymaker join forces to wreak havoc on the most vulnerable victims. Who will they prey upon next? Will you escape or become their next target?
